{"tid":1999014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國經濟顧問庫德洛 表示不會取消對中國履行償債義務","createTime":"2020-05-03T00:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T01:30:02.000Z","uid":98232,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"17d3de555fbb7d0375524ffb0f219d75efd10c3c","tid":1999014,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T00:23:46.000Z","msg":"有消息人士認為，美國現時仍向中國採購個人防護物資，因此推出懲罰措施可能影響採購和貿易協議，所以必須作周詳考慮。<br />\n<br />\n白宮經濟顧問庫德洛（Larry Kudlow）則否認有關媒體報道說：「答案是完全不會（取消對中國履行償債義務）。」<br />\n<br />\n他說：「美債義務的完全信任和信用是神聖不可侵犯，而與此同時，這包括美國維持美元作為全球儲備貨幣。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普亦表示可以向中國實施關稅，而無需走到取消償還美債這一步。他認為中國可能無法阻止疫情擴散，或是故意這樣做，但拒絕表態就中國國家主席習近平是否要為疫情負責，惟他指與疫情相比，中美貿易協議已是次要。<br />\n<br />\n英國路透社及美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）4月30日分別引述消息人士報道，指國務院、白宮國家安全委員會（National Security Council）、財政部及國防部等華府部門正考慮面向中國的不同方案。"},{"pid":"b1bf1c27b4a5efbd5b2b86f459b606a5692155f6","tid":1999014,"uid":98232,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T00:26:14.000Z","msg":"果d話可以取消美債既無腦連登仔 <br />\n睇一睇呢遍文 人地經濟顧問都話唔會咁做<br />\n如果可以咁做 質易戰一早用左啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本用美債制裁中國係無可能既事"},{"pid":"798fb39ee592bc62b77f8eb29f4f6a015a6da247","tid":1999014,"uid":98232,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T00:27:30.000Z","msg":"連登仔真係無撚腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1033bcfdf2cc03088eae6777e973b2be7931b5d","tid":1999014,"uid":26253,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"798fb39ee592bc62b77f8eb29f4f6a015a6da247","tid":1999014,"uid":98232,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T00:27:30.000Z","msg":"連登仔真係無撚腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T00:33:33.000Z","msg":"兒登仔真係當現實生活係打機咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f509bc8403a562c5a3d6b2e202a9e2a481d567","tid":1999014,"uid":79704,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T00:39:07.000Z","msg":"一日未打仗, 一日都唔會做到咁絕. <br />\n<br />\n如果有一日要收到一萬億美債, 就唔會只收美債, 一定會收埋中國的官收係美國的錢. 是但搵個洗黑錢既原因就可以無限期凍結你既錢 (呢招係學黑警搞星火既), 到時就唔係一萬億, 係幾萬億."},{"pid":"c65d45c2b8af2823141229e440b5bb217d420ffe","tid":1999014,"uid":37722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T00:46:10.000Z","msg":"Link又無咩都無<br />\n<br />\n想幫你都幫唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\